The Splunk OpenTelemetry Collector for VMware Tanzu deploys the Splunk OpenTelemetry Collector to connect
to the Loggregator Firehose, forwarding metrics to the Splunk Observability Cloud. This allows
Splunk Observability Cloud users to monitor their Cloud Foundry deployment and applications.

